       Gremlin took one shot in the leg, he slid to the side, avoiding the 
others. In his raptor beast mode, he ran forward, claws extended, and lept 
for Drillbit.

       Jackles front tooth slide out of place. In return, he slipped a knife 
from his belt and drove it for Drillbits neck.

       Pheniox easily managed to avoid the clumsy shots by Dollen. Taking on 
two opponents at once could bring any bot to the point of hysteria. She was 
now grounded, and with a flame launcher in towe, sent a stream of fire at him.

       Nighteyes, from the south of his, is hit in her shoulder once afian, 
sending a chunk of her arm into the matrix. She cursed, and fired, now more 
relentlessly, at Dollen.

--part1_56.568b193.278530d4_boundary
